        This plot shows a bivariate normal scatterplot with 
        <Katex src="\\htmlStyle{font-size: .85rem}{\\sigma_x=1, \\sigma_y=1.5,\\rho=.5}" :inline="true"></Katex> with the covariance ellipse axes and related regression lines. Population slopes are shown, the lines are not subject to sampling variation.
